oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Postcards of the front
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three postcards depicting scenes of the front. First, A German charge, fixed bayonets, photo taken from American lines, France. Second, American heavy artillery moving into action- France. Third, Americans advance, wounded and dying Germans spread along the road. Belleau Wood-France. The Chicago Daily News produced these postcards.
